        },
        {
          "name": "manifest.json",
          "size": 345
        }
      ],
      "author": "joeyuping",
      "description": "- fixed #11 bug for custom shorthand => typing Greek letter shorthand will keep a space behind the expression.\r\n- added {} support for custom shorthand => for expression ending with {}, cursor will be placed within the {} bracket. eg. type sq followed by space will replace with \\sqrt{} and put cursor within the brackets.",
