      "author": "joeyuping",
      "description": "- fixed autoEncloseBrackets timing issue #5 \r\n- Added autoEncloseSubscript function #10 \r\n- Added encloseSelection function - Select an expression and press \"{\", \"[\" or \"(\" key will automatically enclose the expression with the brackets.\r\n\r\nHuge thanks to @infinityiowastaken for the above suggestions!",
